Yuehai Town Government Cadres)

348
00:28:08,180 --> 00:28:09,299
Have you seen my dad?

349
00:28:11,064 --> 00:28:15,000
♪No one can understand your fervor♪

350
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:18,968
♪Your persistence♪

351
00:28:18,968 --> 00:28:23,032
♪You're the gentle passage of a book♪

352
00:28:23,256 --> 00:28:27,768
♪You're the wind-stirred river
of my heart♪

353
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:31,960
♪The loneliness left by old dreams♪

354
00:28:33,075 --> 00:28:37,592
♪Leaving traces, yet shying away♪

355
00:28:38,940 --> 00:28:39,980
I saw you.

356
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:53,880
♪Your silhouette
still lingers before my eyes♪

357
00:28:54,040 --> 00:28:57,016
♪Your promise is deep in my heart♪

358
00:28:58,200 --> 00:29:00,664
♪Remembering your tenderness♪

359
00:29:00,664 --> 00:29:05,848
♪Memories won't let me go♪

360
00:29:06,968 --> 00:29:11,247
♪You're the gentle passage of a book♪

361
00:29:11,247 --> 00:29:14,904
♪Sweeping me away like a gust of wind♪

362
00:29:15,832 --> 00:29:19,672
♪Like a dream
leaving only loneliness upon waking♪

