♪I only remember you came♪

386
00:31:42,968 --> 00:31:46,360
(Even after falling a million times,
we never thought of giving up.)

387
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:47,736
(This is Yuehai.)

388
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:00,760
(Quanmei Cinema)

389
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:58,776
(Snack Store)

390
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:12,259
Am I late?

391
00:33:13,339 --> 00:33:13,940
Not at all.

392
00:33:15,059 --> 00:33:16,019
It's never late.

393
00:33:17,016 --> 00:33:21,208
(Hello, audience)

394
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,139
Mr. Zheng.

395
00:34:47,380 --> 00:34:47,980
Desheng.

396
00:34:51,579 --> 00:34:52,059
Desheng.

397
00:34:54,860 --> 00:34:55,780
Sis-in-law.

398
00:34:57,019 --> 00:34:57,940
These past few years...

399
00:35:00,099 --> 00:35:00,499
Desheng.

400
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:02,460
How many times have you come?

401
00:35:03,499 --> 00:35:05,780
Every time you just stood at the door
without coming in.

402
00:35:06,579 --> 00:35:07,928
You just looked around out here.

403
00:35:08,099 --> 00:35:10,420
You never saw this place as your home.

404
00:35:12,059 --> 00:35:12,539
Desheng.

405
00:35:13,300 --> 00:35:15,619
That's not true.

406
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:19,832
Where's my sister-in-law?

407
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:21,139
She moved away.

408
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:23,579
Moved away?

409
00:35:24,420 --> 00:35:25,300
Where did she move?

410
00:35:25,699 --> 00:35:27,499
To the newly built Dongfu Road.

411
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:29,940
I'll also move there soon.

412
00:35:32,499 --> 00:35:32,888
What?

413
00:35:33,912 --> 00:35:35,539
You thought I'd leave Yuehai?

414
00:35:40,019 --> 00:35:42,699
I'm staying for two reasons.

415
00:35:43,780 --> 00:35:44,664
First,

416
00:35:45,784 --> 00:35:47,460
it's you who never came back.

417
00:35:48,740 --> 00:35:51,420
Second, it's Zhiqiang. He...

418
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,659
He called a few days ago.

419
00:35:54,780 --> 00:35:57,579
He said he could be back next month.

420
00:35:58,699 --> 00:36:00,420
Yes, I know.

421
00:36:01,499 --> 00:36:02,840
He's doing well in there,

422
00:36:03,064 --> 00:36:04,539
so could be out early.

423
00:36:08,740 --> 00:36:10,019
Take one last look

424
00:36:11,980 --> 00:36:14,460
at this old house. Keep it as a memory.

425
00:36:19,288 --> 00:36:21,688
(Serve the country loyally)

426
00:36:22,340 --> 00:36:23,619
Go over there.

427
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:25,139
Careful.

428
00:36:25,499 --> 00:36:26,420
Let me measure you.

429
00:36:31,019 --> 00:36:32,619
You won't grow any taller,

430
00:36:36,659 --> 00:36:37,619
but you've grown

431
00:36:38,900 --> 00:36:39,940
quite a few gray hairs.

432
00:36:53,499 --> 00:36:56,300
(I still remember the first time
I walked into this compound)

433
00:36:56,980 --> 00:36:59,340
(was after I lost the election
for Secretary of Yuehai.)

434
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:03,619
(My heart was filled with longing.)

435
00:37:04,260 --> 00:37:06,139
(Longing to be part of Yuehai.)

436
00:37:06,619 --> 00:37:08,099
(Longing to use my own efforts)

437
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,499
(to turn this marshland into a city.)

438
00:37:12,780 --> 00:37:14,340
(Now I can proudly say)

439
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:17,260
(Yuehai has become a city.)

440
00:37:18,139 --> 00:37:19,619
(But this is never the end.)

441
00:37:20,219 --> 00:37:22,300
(It's the start of a new journey.)

442
00:37:50,099 --> 00:37:50,780
(Meeting time!)

443
00:37:51,179 --> 00:37:52,659
(Excuse me, who are you?)

444
00:37:53,260 --> 00:37:54,179
(I'm Tan Guangming.)

445
00:37:54,539 --> 00:37:56,820
("Tan" as in Tan Sitong,
"Guangming" as in light.)

446
00:37:56,940 --> 00:37:57,740
(Hello, Guangming.)

447
00:38:06,019 --> 00:38:06,820
(Gatekeeper)
(Coming!)

448
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:08,824
(Hello, everyone.)

449
00:38:09,368 --> 00:38:11,059
(Attention. I'm broadcasting a notice.)

450
00:38:16,579 --> 00:38:17,380
(Mr. Zheng.)

451
00:38:17,659 --> 00:38:19,579
(Clinic)
(Your systolic pressure is over 140.)

452
00:38:19,619 --> 00:38:20,420
(Be careful.)

453
00:38:28,380 --> 00:38:30,659
(Three deputies?)

454
00:38:30,900 --> 00:38:31,740
(Who's in charge?)

455
00:38:34,260 --> 00:38:36,539
(We toast to victory together.)

456
00:38:36,539 --> 00:38:37,460
(Li Qiuping as Mayor?)

457
00:38:37,619 --> 00:38:39,860
(Does she know anything
about engineering?)

458
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:40,900
(For such a huge matter!)

459
00:38:41,619 --> 00:38:42,860
(You know the reason best.)

460
00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:43,619
(Xuemei's idea.)

461
00:38:43,619 --> 00:38:44,219
(Stop arguing!)

462
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:45,699
(As the acting mayor...)

463
00:38:45,860 --> 00:38:46,900
(Act lawlessly.)

464
00:39:04,099 --> 00:39:07,019
(We have only one demand. Refund!)

465
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:09,179
(You handled it in a rough way.)

466
00:39:09,380 --> 00:39:10,579
(It can't solve the problem.)

467
00:39:11,980 --> 00:39:12,940
(You must give way.)

468
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:15,499
(Do it with me, and your body
will feel more relaxed.)

469
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:28,312
(Yuehai Government Cadre Bulletin Board)

470
00:39:38,936 --> 00:39:40,260
(Town Mayor's Office)

471
00:39:40,260 --> 00:39:41,340
(Want to fight?)

472
00:39:41,499 --> 00:39:42,456
(Hit me then!)

473
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:43,340
(Shut it.)

474
00:39:43,340 --> 00:39:44,780
(Without city construction fees,)

475
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:46,219
(Yuehai couldn't have been built.)

476
00:39:46,260 --> 00:39:46,980
(What did you do?)

477
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:48,499
(Me again, Wang Lili.)

478
00:39:48,659 --> 00:39:49,380
(Tan.)

479
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:26,648
(Take Pride in Hygiene,
Shame in Neglecting It)

480
00:40:55,300 --> 00:40:57,139
The Yuehai Gift Mall is opening soon.

481
00:40:57,139 --> 00:40:57,619
Thanks.

482
00:40:57,619 --> 00:40:58,380
Please take a look.

483
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:01,059
The Yuehai Gift Mall is opening soon.

484
00:41:01,059 --> 00:41:02,699
The Yuehai Gift Mall is opening soon.

485
00:41:02,699 --> 00:41:04,248
- Please take a look.
- Okay, thanks.

486
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:06,659
The Yuehai Gift Mall is opening soon.

487
00:41:06,820 --> 00:41:07,139
Here.

488
00:41:07,139 --> 00:41:08,099
Okay, I'll get one more.

489
00:41:10,099 --> 00:41:11,340
Give me one too.

490
00:41:18,740 --> 00:41:21,219
It seems our wishes
are coming true one by one.

491
00:41:22,099 --> 00:41:24,499
There's another wish
that will soon come true too.

492
00:41:25,460 --> 00:41:26,099
What is it?

493
00:41:26,539 --> 00:41:28,179
The town government
is actively promoting

494
00:41:28,420 --> 00:41:30,488
the application
for upgrading from a town to a city.

495
00:41:30,659 --> 00:41:31,539
Wonderful!

496
00:41:33,940 --> 00:41:35,260
Time really flies.

497
00:41:35,579 --> 00:41:37,860
I still remember the day we first met.

498
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:40,380
It was quite tense.

499
00:41:40,699 --> 00:41:42,264
Indeed, little man.

500
00:41:45,499 --> 00:41:46,340
Starting today,

501
00:41:47,460 --> 00:41:49,752
this city is in your hands.

502
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:55,099
Goodbye, Li Qiuping.

503
00:41:57,980 --> 00:42:00,420
It's been a pleasure
building this city with you.

504
00:42:01,579 --> 00:42:03,940
My fellow, let's meet
at the next crossroads.

505
00:42:09,699 --> 00:42:11,420
The Yuehai Gift Mall is opening soon.

506
00:42:11,539 --> 00:42:12,539
Please take a look.

507
00:42:12,900 --> 00:42:14,380
Yes, there's a wide variety inside.

508
00:42:16,024 --> 00:42:20,248
♪Step by step towards the spring♪

509
00:42:20,499 --> 00:42:22,099
The Yuehai Gift Mall is opening soon.

510
00:42:22,296 --> 00:42:25,336
♪Nothing can block my way♪

511
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:30,149
♪Perhaps in that future place♪

512
00:42:30,342 --> 00:42:32,504
♪We can meet♪

513
00:42:32,504 --> 00:42:34,648
♪That familiar face again♪

514
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:10,990
♪Gently holding your face♪

515
00:43:13,340 --> 00:43:18,588
♪To dry the tears from your eyes♪

516
00:43:20,148 --> 00:43:25,341
♪My heart will always be yours♪

517
00:43:27,156 --> 00:43:32,492
♪Tell me you'll never be alone again♪

518
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:38,108
♪Gazing deep into your eyes♪

519
00:43:41,028 --> 00:43:46,397
♪No further words are needed♪

520
00:43:48,033 --> 00:43:53,238
♪Tightly holding your hand♪

521
00:43:54,972 --> 00:44:00,332
♪The warmth has never changed♪

522
00:44:01,448 --> 00:44:04,556
♪We share the joy♪

523
00:44:04,884 --> 00:44:08,108
♪We share the pain♪

524
00:44:08,362 --> 00:44:13,933
♪We hold the same hope deep inside♪

525
00:44:15,373 --> 00:44:18,372
♪We brave the storm♪

526
00:44:18,892 --> 00:44:21,884
♪We share the quest♪

527
00:44:22,325 --> 00:44:28,268
♪We cherish this love we share♪

528
00:44:31,458 --> 00:44:36,514
♪Whether we've ever met before♪

529
00:44:38,419 --> 00:44:43,829
♪Be it near or far away♪

530
00:44:45,420 --> 00:44:50,603
♪My heartfelt wish for you♪

531
00:44:52,387 --> 00:44:57,517
♪Is for your peace and happiness♪

532
00:44:58,824 --> 00:45:01,994
♪We share the joy♪

533
00:45:02,252 --> 00:45:05,320
♪We share the pain♪

534
00:45:05,744 --> 00:45:11,967
♪We hold the same hope deep inside♪

535
00:45:12,567 --> 00:45:15,630
♪We brave the storm♪

536
00:45:15,966 --> 00:45:19,054
♪We share the quest♪

537
